 585         public ForStatementNode(const System.Lex.Span& span_, StatementNode* initS_, Node* condition_, StatementNode* loopS_, StatementNode* actionS_) : 
 586             base(NodeType.forStatementNode, span_), initS(initS_), condition(condition_), loopS(loopS_), actionS(actionS_)
 587         {
 588             initS->SetParent(this);
 589             if (!condition.IsNull())
 590             {
 591                 condition->SetParent(this);
 592             }
 593             loopS->SetParent(this);
 594             actionS->SetParent(this);
 595         }

 652         public override Node* Clone(CloneContext& cloneContext) const
 653         {
 654             Node* clonedCondition = null;
 655             if (!condition.IsNull())
 656             {
 657                 clonedCondition = condition->Clone(cloneContext);
 658             }
 659             ForStatementNode* clone = new ForStatementNode(GetSpan(), cast<StatementNode*>(initS->Clone(cloneContext)), clonedCondition, cast<StatementNode*>(loopS->Clone(cloneContext)), cast<StatementNode*>(actionS->Clone(cloneContext)));
 660             clone->SetLeftParenSpan(leftParenSpan);
 661             clone->SetRightParenSpan(rightParenSpan);

 664         public override void Accept(Visitor& visitor)
 665         {
 666             visitor.Visit(*this);
 667         }
 668         public override void Write(AstWriter& writer)
 669         {
 670             base->Write(writer);
 671             writer.Write(initS.Get());
 672             bool hasCondition = condition != null;
 673             writer.GetBinaryWriter().Write(hasCondition);
 674             if (hasCondition)
 675             {
 676                 writer.Write(condition.Get());
 677             }
 678             writer.Write(loopS.Get());
 679             writer.Write(actionS.Get());
 680             writer.Write(leftParenSpan);
 681             writer.Write(rightParenSpan);
 682         }
 683         public override void Read(AstReader& reader)
 684         {
 685             base->Read(reader);
 686             initS.Reset(reader.ReadStatementNode());
 687             initS->SetParent(this);
 688             bool hasCondition = reader.GetBinaryReader().ReadBool();
 689             if (hasCondition)
 690             {
 691                 condition.Reset(reader.ReadNode());
 692                 condition->SetParent(this);
 693             }
 694             loopS.Reset(reader.ReadStatementNode());
 695             loopS->SetParent(this);
 696             actionS.Reset(reader.ReadStatementNode());
 697             actionS->SetParent(this);
 698             leftParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 699             rightParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 700         }
 701         private UniquePtr<StatementNode> initS;
 702         private UniquePtr<Node> condition;
 703         private UniquePtr<StatementNode> loopS;
 704         private UniquePtr<StatementNode> actionS;
